text: Böblingen (; Swabian German: Beblenga) is a town in the German state of Baden- Württemberg. It is the capital of the district Böblingen. In Böblingen the Panzer Kaserne a US Army Marine (military) Corps Military base, are stationed. == References == == Other websites == * * Official website of the town of Böblingen Category:Böblingen (district)
